(WIP)
Idea: Natural Predators of Archkin, caradels are phantasmal entities made of souls that leak out from Nul Detta and bleeded into the plane of existence. Due to the entropy experienced by their souls, virtually all caradel are incapable of speech and barely capable of free will, with notable exceptions, such as Fracturing Mirages, Thronus Caradels (technically), and Echo Caradels.

They respond to distressed/weakened archkin and can be summoned directly through either Fracturing Fissures or Nulgraven Tumors.
Fracturing Caradels are often more logical, featuring more complex capabilities to think, but a clear inability to act on their own.
NulGraven Caradels, in comparison, can function with basic instructions, but are highly emotion and instinct-driven.

Fracturing (cyan):

Verb.
Process.
Ongoing action.
Neutral.

NulGraven (red):

Compound noun.
Feels ancient.
Feels deliberate.
Feels carved.

Fracturing feels like physics.
NulGraven feels like intention.